#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.cov.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.cov"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:1 of
msgid "Compute pairwise covariance of columns, excluding NA/null values."
msgstr "计算各列之间的协方差，排除 NA/null 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:3 of
msgid ""
"Compute the pairwise covariance among the series of a DataFrame. The "
"returned data frame is the `covariance matrix "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covariance_matrix>`__ of the columns of "
"the DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"计算 DataFrame 中各 Series 之间的两两协方差。返回的数据帧是 DataFrame "
"各列的 `协方差矩阵 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covariance_matrix>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:8 of
msgid ""
"Both NA and null values are automatically excluded from the calculation. "
"(See the note below about bias from missing values.) A threshold can be "
"set for the minimum number of observations for each value created. "
"Comparisons with observations below this threshold will be returned as "
"``NaN``."
msgstr ""
"计算中会自动排除 NA 和 null 值。（参见下文关于缺失值带来的偏差说明。）"
"可以设置一个阈值，用于指定每对列之间有效结果所需的最小观测数量。低于此"
"阈值的比较将返回 ``NaN``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:14 of
msgid ""
"This method is generally used for the analysis of time series data to "
"understand the relationship between different measures across time."
msgstr "此方法通常用于时间序列数据分析，以了解不同度量之间随时间变化的关系。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:18 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations required per pair of columns to have a "
"valid result."
msgstr "每对列之间需要的最小观测数量，以获得有效结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:21 of
msgid ""
"Delta degrees of freedom.  The divisor used in calculations is ``N - "
"ddof``, where ``N`` represents the number of elements. This argument is "
"applicable only when no ``nan`` is in the dataframe."
msgstr ""
"自由度调整量。计算中使用的除数是 ``N - ddof``，其中 ``N`` 表示元素数量。"
"此参数仅在 DataFrame 中没有 ``nan`` 时适用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:25 of
msgid "Include only `float`, `int` or `boolean` data."
msgstr "仅包含 `float`、`int` 或 `boolean` 类型的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:28 of
msgid "The covariance matrix of the series of the DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 中各 Series 的协方差矩阵。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:34 of
msgid "Compute covariance with another Series."
msgstr "计算与另一个 Series 的协方差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`core.window.ewm.ExponentialMovingWindow.cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:37 of
msgid "Exponential weighted sample covariance."
msgstr "指数加权样本协方差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`core.window.expanding.Expanding.cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:40 of
msgid "Expanding sample covariance."
msgstr "扩展样本协方差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`core.window.rolling.Rolling.cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:43 of
msgid "Rolling sample covariance."
msgstr "滚动样本协方差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:46 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:47 of
msgid ""
"Returns the covariance matrix of the DataFrame's time series. The "
"covariance is normalized by N-ddof."
msgstr "返回 DataFrame 时间序列的协方差矩阵。协方差通过 N-ddof 进行标准化。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:50 of
msgid ""
"For DataFrames that have Series that are missing data (assuming that data"
" is `missing at random "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missing_data#Missing_at_random>`__) the "
"returned covariance matrix will be an unbiased estimate of the variance "
"and covariance between the member Series."
msgstr ""
"对于包含缺失数据的 Series 的 DataFrame（假设数据是 `随机缺失 <https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Missing_data#Missing_at_random>`__），返回的协方差矩阵"
"是对成员 Series 之间方差和协方差的无偏估计。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:56 of
msgid ""
"However, for many applications this estimate may not be acceptable "
"because the estimate covariance matrix is not guaranteed to be positive "
"semi-definite. This could lead to estimate correlations having absolute "
"values which are greater than one, and/or a non-invertible covariance "
"matrix. See `Estimation of covariance matrices "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Estimation_of_covariance_ "
"matrices>`__ for more details."
msgstr ""
"然而，对于许多应用场景，这种估计可能不可接受，因为估计的协方差矩阵不一定"
"为正半定矩阵。这可能导致估计的相关系数绝对值大于 1，和/或协方差矩阵不可逆"
"。更多信息请参见 `协方差矩阵估计 <https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?"
"title=Estimation_of_covariance_matrices>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:65 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:86 of
msgid "**Minimum number of periods**"
msgstr "**最小周期数**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_dataframe:88 of
msgid ""
"This method also supports an optional ``min_periods`` keyword that "
"specifies the required minimum number of non-NA observations for each "
"column pair in order to have a valid result:"
msgstr ""
"此方法还支持一个可选的 ``min_periods`` 参数，用于指定每对列之间需要的最小"
"非 NA 观测数量，以便获得有效结果："

